Package gov.gsa.pivconformance.cardlib.card.client

Class DataModelSingleton

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.gsa.pivconformance.cardlib.card.client.DataModelSingleton
  • public class DataModelSingleton
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used indirectly by the test atoms. It instantiates some known SP 800-73 rules. Initially being used to manage the container lengths in Tables 8-43.
